{"tid":439428,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟發明時、分、秒之前d人對時間係點既概念","createTime":"2017-10-17T20:08:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T14:56:21.000Z","uid":18468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"aeb68d41586d560f8ce5927bafb8361090441b64","tid":439428,"uid":18468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T20:08:21.000Z","msg":"例如d原始人有語言之後<br />\n但未發明時分秒之前<br />\n佢地溝通既時候係點樣共同定義時間既長短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb9209e71289aa14483b02033f7d32dc2a0e725","tid":439428,"uid":27416,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T20:11:30.000Z","msg":"影子"},{"pid":"736ba0ee74f2eecdf6a9d1eb7c46603e44cfaf62","tid":439428,"uid":40550,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T20:13:04.000Z","msg":"能不能給我一枝香既時間"},{"pid":"97d5865a8e1a7671cf5cf0dbad7fb6974e3fc3ae","tid":439428,"uid":18468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T20:14:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>影子</blockquote><br />\n但佢地當時應該未有東南西北呢個概念<br />\n應該判斷唔到影子既方位同時間既關係"},{"pid":"d0d020660246e8d85530d2684e2e546c41eaf5c2","tid":439428,"uid":18468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T20:15:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>能不能給我一枝香既時間</blockquote><br />\n香應該好遲先有下嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講緊原始人時代"},{"pid":"38e4f62158333fc800108e03304cd30b1353a3eb","tid":439428,"uid":74876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T22:24:08.000Z","msg":"無架，彈指你又知唔知係幾耐？"},{"pid":"14df4c797c39cf94e5c04238c23bf0afeba5cc61","tid":439428,"uid":74876,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T22:25:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無架，彈指你又知唔知係幾耐？</blockquote><br />\n董其昌《畫禪室隨筆》云：「達摩西來，一門超出，而億劫修持三千相，彈指了之。」《摩訶僧祇律》記載：「一剎那者為一念，二十念為一瞬，二十瞬為一彈指，二十彈指為一羅預，二十羅預為一須臾，一日一夜有三十須臾。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n維基"},{"pid":"a7284b6eed1850c4458fb61a47fa2ed1cb31f14d","tid":439428,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T22:35:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無架，彈指你又知唔知係幾耐？</blockquote><br />\n岩岩試過<br />\n三至四個彈指為一秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fe7f0aadcc900365c12dcf004627556868cfc63","tid":439428,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T22:37:28.000Z","msg":"留名等人話人發明時間單位之前時間唔存在"},{"pid":"ee9375b1fd0d9657db6ffec9eb2d81e385bd0f41","tid":439428,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T22:43:52.000Z","msg":"咁不如問佢地有冇時間呢種概念<br />\n定係只有天光天黑的概念"},{"pid":"2aceb4749e134b629e4de020e9289842f22931be","tid":439428,"uid":18468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:55:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無架，彈指你又知唔知係幾耐？</blockquote><br />\n岩岩試過<br />\n三至四個彈指為一秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁有d人彈快d有d人彈慢d點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c666145aaeb46a602448266b7a1a574a60dd4fd","tid":439428,"uid":18468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:57:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁不如問佢地有冇時間呢種概念<br />\n定係只有天光天黑的概念</blockquote><br />\n咁應該都要有時間既概念先可以容許到做某d群體活動 例如要同人講半個鐘後食飯 問題係原始人點表達半個鐘呢個概念"},{"pid":"0a39a1b8789bf223ff01fd14c27c8fbe66d58de9","tid":439428,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T06:32:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無架，彈指你又知唔知係幾耐？</blockquote><br />\n岩岩試過<br />\n三至四個彈指為一秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁有d人彈快d有d人彈慢d點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係唔公平架啦<br />\n你覺得時間唔夠用咪彈番慢D囉"},{"pid":"a7f03712e6ee154af7b886ad528a0c9eab406653","tid":439428,"uid":39463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T06:36:43.000Z","msg":"未有準確時間觀念之前，應該冇辦法預定咁多工作，先後次序唔同"},{"pid":"5d52a470ec8088e14825405b2990430e